# ST8 Identity System
.st8/

# ST8 runtime artifacts — regenerated every `node start.js .` run.
# Timestamped indexer snapshots (e.g. 2026-05-15T11-18-23-245Z_*.txt) and
# the LATEST_*.txt symlink-equivalents are pure runtime output. Hand-curated
# planning docs (00_*, 01_*, EXECUTION-PLAN.md, PRD.md, etc.) stay tracked.
.planning/st8_identity_system/*Z_*
.planning/st8_identity_system/LATEST_*

# Live connection state — written on every boot, dominates diffs otherwise.
connection-state.json